snippet.title: Flynguin Station - Trailer / Indie Game 2019
snippet.description: Flynguin Station is a casual projectile-endless runner game with RPG elements. Save the penguins by re-discovering the secrets of flight! Fly as far as possible, level up, upgrade your penguin and customize him to your liking.
